### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">هُوَ ٱلَّذِى جَعَلَ لَكُمُ ٱلَّيْلَ لِتَسْكُنُوا۟ فِيهِ وَٱلنَّهَارَ مُبْصِرًا ۚ إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَـٰتٍ لِّقَوْمٍ يَسْمَعُونَ</span>

### English

He is the One Who has made the night for you to rest in and the day bright. Surely in this are signs for people who listen.